com.bertramlabs.plugins.karman
[Groovy] Interface CloudFileInterface

interface CloudFileInterface

An Interface for interacting with Cloud Files. If looking to add new cloud providers, one must implement this interface via the {@com.bertramlabs.plugins.karman.CloudFile} abstract class.
